scenes.description: Mori Calliope, Takanashi Kiara, and Ninomae Ina'nis share their closing thoughts and thank the fans during the 5th anniversary stream.
The members announce and showcase special 5th anniversary merchandise including acrylic panels, cards, medals, and hats.
Display of handwritten thank you messages from each member of hololive English -Myth-.
Outro screen with the 'Fortune Spinner' logo.
